1
00:01:03,630 --> 00:01:05,860
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,150 --> 00:01:09,750
[Episode 11]

3
00:01:11,170 --> 00:01:13,710
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

4
00:01:17,430 --> 00:01:19,760
Madam, your tea is here.

5
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:27,430
You fool!

6
00:01:27,430 --> 00:01:28,890
Are you trying to scald me?

7
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,310
Madam,

8
00:01:30,510 --> 00:01:32,350
I didn't pour this tea.

9
00:01:33,950 --> 00:01:35,150
How dare you talk back!

10
00:01:35,150 --> 00:01:36,479
Everything you eat and drink

11
00:01:36,479 --> 00:01:37,640
is from the Jiang family.

12
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:39,479
You're nothing but a dog
kept by the Jiang family.

13
00:01:39,479 --> 00:01:42,789
You used to follow Jiang Li around
disrespecting your elders every day,

14
00:01:42,789 --> 00:01:44,039
showing no respect.

15
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,280
Today,

16
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:47,350
I will teach you

17
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:49,350
the proper rules of being a servant.

18
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:05,350
My Lady.

19
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,280
Listen to me carefully.

20
00:02:10,910 --> 00:02:12,470
Xi'er belongs to me.

21
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:14,750
You want to punish her?

22
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,470
You have no right!

23
00:02:19,470 --> 00:02:21,079
Jiang Li, why...

24
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,750
Why are you back?

25
00:02:22,870 --> 00:02:25,270
As your elder, I'm disciplining a servant.

26
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,860
How does that concern you?

27
00:02:27,079 --> 00:02:28,240
Could it be

28
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:30,710
you're still upset
about the arranged marriage?

29
00:02:30,710 --> 00:02:33,970
Your father and I are only
thinking of your best interests.

30
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,680
What are you doing?

31
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,760
Aren't you tired of pretending?

32
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,600
I'm tired of listening to it.

33
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:51,800
How about this:

34
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,400
I might as well make it real.

35
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:55,520
I'll truly be the villain for once,

36
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:59,120
so you can genuinely feel wronged.

37
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,190
Don't do anything rash!

38
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:01,840
Someone come! Help!

39
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,870
Stop shouting.

40
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,910
My hands

41
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:07,680
are much quicker
than your help will arrive.

42
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,120
I was wrong.

43
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:12,030
Li, please spare me.

44
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,880
Apologize to Xi'er!

45
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,630
I'm sorry.

46
00:03:17,190 --> 00:03:18,430
My Lady.

47
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:19,240
Forget it.

48
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,280
Xi'er, don't be afraid.

49
00:03:27,470 --> 00:03:28,870
I'm here to take you away.

50
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:30,560
From now on,

51
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,340
we'll live in Chunliu Garden.

52
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:35,140
We'll never come back here again.

53
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:39,520
Are you alright, Madam?

54
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,360
She's terrifying.

55
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:01,840
May I ask what brings

56
00:04:02,310 --> 00:04:03,710
Your Majesty here today?

57
00:04:08,910 --> 00:04:09,680
Mother.

58
00:04:10,310 --> 00:04:12,630
Does this look familiar to you?

59
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,850
I don't practice martial arts.

60
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,850
How would I recognize such a thing?

61
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,920
The iron of this arrowhead

62
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:25,930
comes from Qingyang Prefecture.

63
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:28,000
I recall

64
00:04:28,270 --> 00:04:30,310
that your natal family's fief

65
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,510
is in Qingyang Prefecture.

66
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:40,130
If Your Majesty has something to say,

67
00:04:40,130 --> 00:04:41,690
please speak plainly.

68
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,680
We may be mother and son,

69
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:49,630
yet this is a crime that calls for
the extermination of an entire clan.

70
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:51,830
This is my final warning.

71
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:53,830
Do not push me any further.

72
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:14,290
It was clearly Xun Simo's
own recklessness,

73
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,750
but unexpectedly,

74
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:17,480
it has implicated you, Mother.

75
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:20,600
I've always known he's impulsive.

76
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,160
I just never expected...

77
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:23,920
Mother,

78
00:05:24,190 --> 00:05:26,630
you and Jiuzhao
are mother and son after all.

79
00:05:26,630 --> 00:05:27,920
Given the circumstances,

80
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:31,000
if you're willing to concede,
there might still be a way out.

81
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:31,870
How dare you!

82
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,840
What do you know about anything?

83
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,750
Everything I did was for you.

84
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:39,190
As for Xie Jiuzhao,

85
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,800
he's a demon,

86
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:46,600
a death warrant hanging over our heads.

87
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,270
I wish

88
00:05:51,190 --> 00:05:53,720
I had never given birth to him.

89
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,120
Nianzhao,

90
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,690
you're different from him.

91
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,240
Trust me.

92
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,040
One day

93
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:09,560
I will make sure you get everything
that should be yours.

94
00:06:15,170 --> 00:06:21,360
[Chunliu Garden]

95
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,390
Thank heaven and earth

96
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:32,720
and His Majesty for helping
my lady reclaim Chunliu Garden.

97
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:39,630
Take them to clean up first.

98
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:41,680
I need some time alone.

99
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:43,870
Yes.

100
00:06:44,270 --> 00:06:45,600
Everyone, come with me.

101
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:27,610
[Chunliu Garden]

102
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,270
Li.

103
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,240
Li.

104
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:03,600
My Li has grown up so much.

105
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:09,720
You're even taller than me now.

106
00:08:12,070 --> 00:08:14,000
I've failed you.

107
00:08:15,190 --> 00:08:16,360
All these years,

108
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:20,920
you've suffered so much.

109
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:24,270
Mother.

110
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,270
Don't worry.

111
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:30,430
No matter how difficult things get,

112
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:33,630
I'll always persevere.

113
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,000
But...

114
00:08:40,150 --> 00:08:40,909
Mother.

115
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:44,630
I've reclaimed Chunliu Garden,

116
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,390
gained my freedom,

117
00:08:46,550 --> 00:08:48,910
and become just like you.

118
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:50,600
But

119
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:54,960
why am I still not happy?

120
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:56,790
Li.

121
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,270
There are things

122
00:08:59,870 --> 00:09:02,000
you must face on your own.

123
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:03,440
I can

124
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:07,120
only accompany you this far.

125
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:11,670
You must go on longer than I ever could—

126
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:13,360
and farther, too.

127
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,910
Be true to yourself,

128
00:09:16,790 --> 00:09:17,720
understand?

129
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,600
[Her cloudlike hair frames a flowered
face; a golden step-shake sways.]

130
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,730
[In jade halls, wine-dazed, she leans
against the balustrade. — Xingzhi]

131
00:09:48,490 --> 00:09:50,230
[Her cloudlike hair frames a flowered
face; a golden step-shake sways.]

132
00:09:50,230 --> 00:09:51,970
[In jade halls, wine-dazed, she leans
against the balustrade. — Xingzhi]

133
00:10:15,380 --> 00:10:16,240
[At court, the various factions
exist in a delicate balance.]

134
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:17,080
[Close coordination between
the Empress and the General's Mansion]

135
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:17,910
[may disrupt the fragile balance of power
and destabilize governance.]
